README:
Data set with resting state fMRI and fMRI task for evaluation of working memory.
Includes data from patients with temporal lobe epilepsy and healthy participants.
Cognitive data is included: Wechsler’s Adult Intelligence Scale (WAIS-IV) and Weschsler’s Memory Scale (WMS-IV).
